## 4.0.0 (2026-06-19)

### New feature:

-   rename the fork to See See with an independent app identity
-   add OCR-free screenshot vision providers in the screenshot translation window
-   add OpenAI-compatible vision service configuration with endpoint presets and custom prompts
-   refresh See See icon assets

### Changed:

-   disable the upstream Pot updater for the fork until See See release signing is configured
-   skip the upstream single-instance plugin in Windows debug builds to avoid the known development startup panic

## 3.0.7 (2025-5-10)

### New feature:

-   signed macOS app

### Bugs fixed:

-   fix screenshot on macOS
-   rm tray click event on macOS
